			<description><![CDATA[<p><strong><span style="font-size: larger; ">100% Work On Your Own Time</span></strong></p>
<p> </p>
<p style="padding-left: 0px; "><span style="font-size: medium; ">About Us:</span></p>
<p><a href="http://www.hookupfeed.com/home.asp">HookUpFeed</a> is an interactive service that offers an innovative approach to mobile marketing and advertisement. Our mission is to <em>deliver each subscriber with the right offer at the right time through the right channel</em>. With HookUpFeed, consumers can browse our extensive network of businesses to find offers that are tailored to their specific interests. On the other side of the picture, merchants can engage with their customers at a higher and more targeted level, by marketing directly to the people that want their product. HookUpFeed will "hook you up" with coupons, sales, and other promotions from all of your favorite retailers.</p>
<p>Getting "Hooked Up" with HookUpFeed is easy. We provide our users with many avenues to seek the perfect deal:</p>
<ul>
<li>Text Message</li>
<li>Email</li>
<li>Direct Print</li>
<li>Social Media Platforms</li>
<li>iPhone (launching in June)</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size: medium; ">Responsibilities</span>:</p>
<ul>
<li>Engage with your potential clients face-to-face to get a better picture of who you will be working with and the businesses you will be managing.</li>
<li>Provide world-class customer support to your clients using avenues that range from email, social networks to phone conversations.</li>
<li>Be an extrovert: HookUpFeed rewards the bold and the brave. The more businesses you talk to = the more clients you sign up = more money monthly in your pocket. </li>
<li>Be attentive: Gather feedback that will inform Engineering, Product, Marketing, and Sales decisions.</li>
</ul>
<p style="padding-left: 0px; "><span style="font-size: medium; ">Requirements:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>0-2 years of business experience with a strong desire to help merchants increase their business. Candidates with a proven track record in sales, marketing, management, or consulting is a plus.</li>
<li>You must be a self-starter with a strong desire to work for yourself alongside the support of a world class team.</li>
<li>You have excellent written and oral communication skills. You maintain your own personal blog or Twitter account and love sharing deals with your friends through social media.</li>
<li>Ability to work and travel independently with unwavering professionalism and high productivity.</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size: medium; ">Compensation:</span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 12px; ">HookUpFeed Agent compensation is based on commission, which means the more vendors you sign up under the HookUpFeed service, the more money you get a month. HookUpFeed charges a flat rate of $119/month for all our vendors, which you get a percentage of every month.</span></span></li>
<li><span style="font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: 12px; ">Entry Level: 15%. This is that level you start at. This means you are signing up 1-3 vendors a month.</span></span></li>
<li>Intermediate Level: 25%. At this level, you are an active agent, signing up 4-7 vendors a month.</li>
<li>HookUp Hero: 30%. At this level, your work is incredible, signing up 8+ vendors a month.</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-size: medium;">Perks:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>We are flexible on time spent for this role. As a HookUpFeed Agent, you are the face of HookUpFeed. As long as you represent our company with professionalism and consistently sign up new vendors at a minimum 1 per 3 months, how ever much you work is fine with us. But remember, the more vendors you sign up means more money in your pocket.</li>
</ul>
<p style="padding-left: 0px; "><span style="font-size: medium; ">How to apply:</span></p>
<ul>
<li>Applications without cover letters will not be considered. We need people who can communicate professionally and intellectually, your cover letter will give us a chance to see you beyond a one page resume.</li>
<li>Please include links to your blog, Twitter, etc. where we can learn more about you and what you believe.</li>
<li>You <em>must </em>be authorized to work in the United States on a full-time basis for any employer. We will not sponsor visas, nor will we hire consultants through sub-contractors that hold your visa.</li>
</ul>
<div style="text-align: left;"><br /></div>
<p>HookUpFeed is looking to recruit a network to promote the services and brands it boasts and we need a team of dedicated agents that will represent our name and bring deals to the community.</p>
<p>Get involved and help bring the best offers from the best merchants near you!</p>]]></description>
